Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrdvrsc] <Ginasis Mining Pools> once the pool finds a block you will be paid a portion of that block in relation to your shares

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrdvrsc] <Ginasis Mining Pools> say all shares on the pool equal to 100% then divide the block by total amount of shares and times that number by your shares minus the 0.75% pool fee and that is your earnings for that block
